<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>ema511_01_IH_0003_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema511_01.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema511_01_ih_0003">
      <section class="title type2 flex_wrap">
        <h2 lang="y">
          <span class="recap" lang="y">이전에 <span>배웠어요</span></span>
        </h2>

        <div class="title_sub">
          <span lang="y">『수학 4-1』 (세 자리 수)× (두 자리 수)의 활용</span>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="3" lang="y">민준이가 줄넘기를 하루에 185회씩 14일 동안 했습니다. 민준이가 줄넘기를 모두 몇 회 했는지 식을 쓰고 답을 구해 보세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="input_area flex justify_center">
          <div class="question_box align_start gap_60">
            <div class="flex align_center gap_12">
              <span lang="y">식:</span>
              <div class="input_wrap answer1">
                <math-field data-answer-single="185×14"></math-field>
              </div>
              <span>=</span>
              <div class="input_wrap answer2">
                <math-field data-answer-single="2590"></math-field>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex align_center">
              <span lang="y">답:</span>
              <div class="input_wrap answer3">
                <math-field data-answer-single="2590"></math-field>
              </div>
              <span lang="y">회</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p lang="y">(민준이가 줄넘기를 한 횟수)</p>
                <p lang="y">=185×14=2590(회)</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
